quran[40]{c,v,t}:
  77,1,By the winds sent forth in swift succession
  77,2,and then storming on with a tempest's force
  77,3,and the rain-spreading winds
  77,4,separating one from another
  77,5,by those who bring down the reminder
  77,6,to excuse some and warn others
  77,7,that which you have been promised shall be fulfilled
  77,8,When the stars lose their light
  77,9,and when the sky is rent asunder
  77,10,and when the mountains crumble into dust
  77,11,and when the messengers are brought together at the appointed time
  77,12,for what Day has this been appointed
  77,13,For the Day of Decision
  77,14,What will explain to you what the Day of Judgement is
  77,15,Woe on that Day to those who reject the truth
  77,16,Did We not destroy the earlier peoples
  77,17,We will now cause the later ones to follow them
  77,18,thus do We deal with the culprits
  77,19,Woe on that Day to those who reject the truth
  77,20,Did We not create you from a humble fluid
  77,21,"then placed it in a secure repository [the womb]"
  77,22,for an appointed term
  77,23,Thus We have determined the stages of development and Our power to determine is excellent indeed
  77,24,Woe on that Day to those who reject the truth
  77,25,Have We not made the earth a receptacle
  77,26,for the living and the dead
  77,27,Have We not placed high mountains upon it and given you fresh water to drink
  77,28,Woe on that Day to those who reject the truth
  77,29,Proceed to that which you denied
  77,30,Proceed to a shadow rising in three columns
  77,31,"affording neither shade, nor protection from the flames"
  77,32,and throwing up sparks as huge as towers
  77,33,and as bright as a herd of yellow camels
  77,34,Woe on that Day to those who reject the truth
  77,35,On that Day they will be speechless
  77,36,nor shall they be permitted to offer excuses
  77,37,Woe on that Day to those who reject the truth
  77,38,This is the Day of Judgement. We have assembled you all together with past generations
  77,39,"If now you have any strategy, use it against Me"
  77,40,Woe on that Day to those who reject the truth